### Posts Pagination Examples

### Get all posts with default pagination (page=1, limit=10)
GET http://localhost:3000/posts

### Get posts with custom pagination - page 2, limit 5
GET http://localhost:3000/posts?page=2&limit=5

### Get posts with only page specified (limit will default to 10)
GET http://localhost:3000/posts?page=3

### Get posts with only limit specified (page will default to 1)
GET http://localhost:3000/posts?limit=20

### Get posts by user with pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/posts/user/1?page=1&limit=5

### Get posts by user with default pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/posts/user/1

