### Error Examples:

### Invalid page number (should be >= 1)
GET http://localhost:3000/posts?page=0

### Invalid limit (should be > 0)
GET http://localhost:3000/posts?limit=0

### Invalid page type (should be integer)
GET http://localhost:3000/posts?page=abc
